 inspire hopeful critiques of an allegedly post-truth society.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Mrz 2024) 0aTruth. 4aJewish Studies : Jewish Studies. 4aPhilosophy : Continental Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Critical Theory. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Individual Philosophers.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package 2024z978311149259940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143849642940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438496429423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438496429/original  a978-3-11-149259-9  SUNY Press eBook Package 2024b2024  aGBV-deGruyter-alles